---
// PressMention - Sección de mención en prensa (El Diario de Andalucía)
// Diseño editorial asimétrico: columna visual oscura + columna contenido clara
---

<section class="section bg-alabaster relative" id="prensa">
  <div class="container-editorial">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="group relative border border-border-delicate bg-cream/20 hover:bg-cream transition-all duration-700 overflow-hidden" data-reveal>
        
        {/* Decoración: comillas grandes de fondo */}
        <span class="absolute top-4 right-6 lg:right-12 font-serif text-[5rem] sm:text-[6rem] lg:text-[10rem] leading-none text-olive/[0.04] font-light select-none group-hover:text-olive/[0.08] transition-colors duration-700" aria-hidden="true">
          "
        </span>

        <div class="relative z-10 grid lg:grid-cols-12 items-stretch">
          
          {/* Columna visual (izquierda) */}
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative bg-ink flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-10 lg:p-14">
            {/* Patrón de puntos sutil */}
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, var(--color-alabaster) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 20px 20px;" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            
            <div class="relative z-10 text-center">
              {/* Icono periódico */}
              <div class="w-16 h-16 lg:w-20 lg:h-20 rounded-full border border-alabaster/20 flex items-center justify-center text-alabaster/80 mx-auto mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:border-alabaster/40 transition-all duration-500">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-7 h-7 lg:w-8 lg:h-8">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 7.5h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m-7.5 3h7.5m-7.5 3h7.5m3-9h3.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V18a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25M16.5 7.5V18a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25M16.5 7.5V4.875c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H4.125C3.504 3.75 3 4.254 3 4.875V18a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h13.5M6 7.5h3v3H6v-3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              
              <p class="text-label-xs text-alabaster/50 tracking-[0.25em] mb-3">MEDIO DIGITAL</p>
              <p class="font-serif text-xl lg:text-2xl text-alabaster leading-tight mb-2">El Diario de Andalucía</p>
              <p class="text-label-xs text-alabaster/40 tracking-wider">ABRIL 2026</p>
              
              {/* Línea decorativa terracotta */}
              <div class="w-10 h-[1px] bg-terracotta-light mx-auto mt-8"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Columna contenido (derecha) */}
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 p-10 sm:p-12 lg:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center relative">
            <div class="mb-6 lg:mb-8">
              <span class="label-section text-olive/80">Mención en prensa</span>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-[2rem] xl:text-4xl text-ink leading-[1.15] mb-6 lg:mb-8">
              Psicología Sanitaria en Córdoba con <em class="text-olive italic">experiencia, rigor y humanidad</em>
            </h3>
            
            <p class="text-body-sm text-charcoal mb-8 lg:mb-10 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
              El Diario de Andalucía ha destacado la trayectoria y el enfoque de la consulta en un artículo dedicado, reconociendo el compromiso con el bienestar emocional de personas, parejas y familias.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-5 sm:gap-8">
              <a 
                href="https://eldiariodeandalucia.com/maria-angeles-mata/" 
                target="_blank" 
                rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                class="btn btn-outline group/btn"
              >
                <span>Leer el artículo</span>
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 transform transition-transform duration-300 group-hover/btn:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.75L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.25M21 12H3" />
                </svg>
              </a>
              
              <span class="text-label-xs text-charcoal/50 tracking-wider">eldiariodeandalucia.com</span>
            </div>

            {/* Línea decorativa animada al hover */}
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-0 h-[2px] bg-olive group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-1000 ease-out"></div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
